Description: CPU load generator with WebUI and REST API
 A tool to generate CPU load on a system with runtime configuration
 through a WebUI and REST API. It supports multiple computation types
 and provides real-time monitoring capabilities.
 .
 Features:
  - Multiple computation types (prime numbers, matrix operations, etc.)
  - WebUI for easy configuration
  - REST API for programmatic control
  - MQTT support for IoT integration
  - Real-time load monitoring
